### Phase 2: Backend API Route Implementation (US-002) ✅
- Created `src/app/api/generate/route.ts` POST endpoint
- Implemented comprehensive input validation:
  - Topic: required, max 200 characters
  - Key points: required, max 2000 characters
  - Tone: must be one of 5 valid options
