- Structured prompt engineering for consistent article generation
- Build verification: PASSED - zero errors

### Phase 3: Frontend Form Component (US-003) ✅
- Converted `src/app/page.tsx` to client component with `'use client'` directive
- Implemented interactive form with:
  - Topic text input with 200 character limit and live counter
  - Key points textarea with 2000 character limit and live counter
  - Tone/style dropdown with 5 options (Professional, Casual, Academic, Creative, Conversational)
  - Client-side validation with error messages
  - Loading state with animated spinner
  - Disabled state during API calls
- Real-time form validation preventing empty submissions
- Character count display for both input fields
- Build verification: PASSED - zero errors

### Phase 4: Results Display and Export (US-004, US-005, US-006) ✅
- Results section displays after successful generation:
