### Phase 5: Form Debouncing and Rate Limiting (US-007) ✅
- Implemented 3-second cooldown between generations
- Error message: "Please wait a few seconds before generating again"
- Users can edit form fields during cooldown period
- Generate button remains enabled but shows error on click during cooldown
- Prevents API abuse and excessive costs
- Build verification: PASSED - zero errors

